This project implements a responsive product showcase section for VR devices using Bootstrap 4 and custom CSS. The layout is designed to highlight product visuals while keeping key information and actions clearly accessible across all screen sizes.

ğŸ§± Layout & Responsiveness

The section is built using Bootstrapâ€™s grid system:

Mobile devices: Product cards stack vertically for optimal readability.

Medium screens: Cards adjust into balanced columns.

Large screens: Two product cards are displayed side by side for efficient use of horizontal space.

Bootstrap utility classes handle spacing and alignment without relying on fixed layouts.

ğŸ–¼ï¸ Product Card Structure

Each product is represented by a full-height visual card that uses a background image rather than an <img> element. This allows text and buttons to be overlaid directly on the image.

Each card contains:

Product title

Price information

Primary call-to-action button

Content is aligned to the bottom of the card to maintain a consistent visual hierarchy.

ğŸ¨ Background Image Handling

Custom CSS controls background rendering for the product cards:

background-size: cover ensures the image fills the card area proportionally.

background-position: center keeps the focal point centered.

Fixed height provides visual consistency between cards.

This approach creates immersive product visuals without layout shifts.

ğŸ“ Content Alignment

Flexbox is used to align text and buttons within each card:

display: flex and flex-direction: column organize content vertically.

justify-content: flex-end anchors content to the bottom of the card.

Internal padding ensures readable spacing from the edges.

âœï¸ Typography & Styling

Google Fonts provide consistent, modern typography.

White text ensures strong contrast against background images.

Buttons are styled with borders and rounded corners to maintain visual clarity.

ğŸ”˜ Action Buttons

Each product card includes a â€œBuy Nowâ€ button styled to match the overall theme.

A separate â€œView Allâ€ button is positioned below the cards and aligned to the right using Flexbox utilities, making it easily discoverable without distracting from the main content.

ğŸ¯ Design Consistency

Consistent card dimensions across products

Unified color palette and typography

Clear visual hierarchy between title, price, and action

